input and expands accordingly. The Wild Hunt -- the estate's
mobile enforcement -- has extended its patrol range toward the
Lantern Road farther than in any prior generation.

If Wild Hunt elements reach trade convoys, the Harbor Wardens
face a classification problem without precedent. Necrotic entities
are not smuggled goods or cursed artifacts -- they are active
hostile process attached to material. The Quarantine Ledger's
four-tier system was designed for objects, not for biological
intelligences that replicate institutional structure in bark
and bone.

The Thornwood Lich retains Lord Harren inside a system he
helped create. This is oath-breaking turned inside out: the
institution consuming the oath-swearer rather than the oath-
swearer betraying the institution. The Shrine of the First
Claw was built to oppose precisely this.

The substrate logic -- crystalline formations mediating the
necrotic ecology -- is a Quarantine Ledger concern. Crystal-
mediated phenomena are flagged in our hazard tables regardless
of origin: unattested geological power interfacing with
institutional decay.

Standing guidance to the Sand-Sea Carters' Guild: any convoy
reporting necrotic contact along the northern route triggers
Tier Two inspection at the Reach boundary. Cargo from the
living is welcome. Cargo from the dead must prove it is not
still serving the dead.

Thornwood holds that death is patient and thorough. We intend
to be swifter.

